pr_body:
This PR contains the initial setup of ElectronJS app with Vuejs framework.

It also has working login and signup frontend pages.
Added the protos for signup, login and frontend pages for login/signup.
Updated gRPC to grpc-web to use browser side client for gRPC communication.

pr_title: working login/signup with userStore and changeable service implementation
pr_body:
Implemented the following
- working login and signup with authentication APIs
- user store using pinia
- services implemented using provide-inject to keep the services dynamic when existing GRPC-web services are implemented in REST

pr_title: dynamic navbar and persisten pinia storage
pr_body:
Added below features:
- logout
- dynamic nav bar before and after login
- user data storage persistent with reload

pr_title: CyberShuttle services implemented with apps view
pr_body:
Following features implemented
- App view has been implemented
- Following APIs were implemented

    - getApps
    - getItems
    - launch item
    - stop item
Item view implemented with working launch and stop items.

This PR contains following updates:
 - It gets details from server about consul params
 - It retains the consul details after every login
This PR contains necessary updates to accommodate orchestration and server interactions via consul.
A few more additions to allow server-orchestration integration
It contains server side code for communications to cybershuttle app.

pr_body:
This PR consists of following updates:
 - It gets connected to consul and operates consul in full permissions mode
 - Upon login user app gets consul parameters sent
 - Upon launch of items server communicates to consul which will lead the orchestration

Added the Orchestration agent with following capabilities
- It connects and controls the nomad agent which does container orchestration
- It has following functions:
  - connect to nomad
  - startJob to initiate a job with nomad
  - killJob to stop a job with nomad
  - listJobs to show all running jobs with nomad
